<guidanceItem id="00000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000724b8" Author="" Category="Administration" Priority="" Rule_Type="Documentation" Status="" Technology="TeamMentor" title="Installing TeamMentor on IIS 6.0" Topic="" phase="NA" libraryId="eb39d862-f752-4d1c-ab6e-14ed697397c0" xmlns="urn:microsoft:guidanceexplorer:guidanceItem">
  <content>
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;If you want to use the application locally only, use Cassini. If you want to expose the application
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;on a web server to your team, use IIS.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;To install TeamMentor on IIS 6:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;font face="Arial, Verdana" size="2"&gt;Copy TeamMentor files to local folder&lt;/font&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Download&amp;nbsp;the .zip&lt;/b&gt; file of TeamMentor and extract it&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;You can also do a &lt;b&gt;
Git Clone&lt;/b&gt; of the desired version of TeamMentor from GitHub&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;b&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;b&gt;TeamMentor root folder&lt;/b&gt; should contain the following folders:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Library_Data - this folder contains the library files.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Web Application - this folder contains the application files.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Add TeamMentor to IIS 6.0.&lt;/b&gt; Open the &amp;quot;Internet Information Services (IIS) Manager&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Navigate to &amp;quot;Web Sites&amp;quot; in the tree on the left of the &amp;quot;Internet Information Services (IIS) &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Manager&amp;quot; window.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Right-click on &amp;quot;Web Sites&amp;quot; and select &amp;quot;New&amp;quot; -&amp;gt; &amp;quot;Web Site...”&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&amp;quot;Web Site Creation Wizard&amp;quot; should appear.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;Next&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Enter a description for the web&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;site, something like &amp;quot;TeamMentor 3&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;Next&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Change the port setting, if necessary.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;Next&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;Browse...”&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Select to the &amp;quot;Web Applications\TM_Website&amp;quot; folder&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;inside the TeamMentor root folder&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;Next&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Check&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;the checkbox next to &amp;quot;Run scripts (such as ASP)&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;Next&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;Finish&amp;quot;. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
A new&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;web site should appear in the tree structure on the left of the &amp;quot;Internet Information&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Services (IIS) Manager&amp;quot; window.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Right-click on this new web site.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Select &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot;. A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot; window should appear.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Go to the &amp;quot;ASP.NET&amp;quot; tab in the &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;window.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Set the .NET version to 2.0. Click &amp;quot;OK&amp;quot;.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
TeamMentor 3 should now be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;operational.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;b&gt;If content or user changes are desired,&lt;/b&gt; the account used by IIS needs to have write privileges to the TeamMentor Root folder&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Identify the application account.&lt;/b&gt; which is the Windows user account used by the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;IIS Application Pool configured on the TeamMentor
 website.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;On the &amp;quot;Internet&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Information Services (IIS) Manager&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Navigate to &amp;quot;Application Pools&amp;quot; in the tree on the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;left.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Right-click on the &amp;quot;Default App Pool&amp;quot; and select &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot;. A &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;window should appear.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Go to the &amp;quot;Identity&amp;quot; tab in the &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot; window. Take note of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;the selected user-name. By default, it is &amp;quot;Network Service&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Adjust the file-system permissions&lt;/b&gt;. Give write permissions for the TeamMentor folder&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;to the Windows user account that is used
 to run TeamMentor. This is the username that&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;has been discovered in the previous step.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Right click on the TeamMentor root folder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Select &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot;. A &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot; window&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;should appear.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Select the &amp;quot;Security&amp;quot; tab in the &amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot; window. Give &amp;quot;Full Access&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;permissions to the Windows account that is used to run TeamMentor.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Verdana; font-size:small"&gt;Click &amp;quot;OK&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</content>
